data.description: 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full bath home in the heart of Mountain Brook. As you enter, there is a foyer, large living room with bay window and separate dining room.  Large den with a wood burning, brick fireplace and open to the kitchen. Remodeled kitchen with granite counter tops, breakfast bar, stainless appliances and lots of cabinets. Hardwood floors throughout living area. Large Master bedroom with a walk-in closet, hardwood floors, and master bath with remodeled tile shower.  2 bedrooms with carpet and walk in closet in one of the bedrooms. Unfinished basement with lots of storage, laundry area, laundry sink, and potential for future expansion/bedrooms.  New Deck which is great for entertaining and relaxing. Small front porch. 2 car carports. Private back yard. Exterior has been newly painted.
